  • public class Pair<A,B>
extends java.lang.Object
    An ordered pair of objects (a, b). (a1, b1).equals(a2, b2) iff (a1 == null && a2 == null || a1.equals(a2)) && (b1 == null && b2 == null || b1.equals(b2))
